title: Wind Cave National Park: Wind Cave Trip Reports
body: Wind Cave Trip Reports         Caver in Southern Comfort Photo by Art Palmer  Wind Cave is mostly explored by cavers who are members of various caving clubs or grottos affiliated with the National Speleological Society. Each off-trail trip into the cave chronicles the explorers discoveries in Wind Cave.   By selecting one of the years listed below, you can follow the exploration of Wind Cave as cavers discover more of the passageways hidden beneath the prairie world of Wind Cave National Park.
